Staircase detail

This is a staircase of size :

   #
  ##
 ###
####
Its base and height are both equal to . It is drawn using # symbols and spaces. The last line is not preceded by any spaces.

Write a program that prints a staircase of size .



def staircase(n):
    for i in range(n):
        print(" " * (n - i - 1), end="")
        print("*" * (i + 1))

staircase(4)
